overview: Highlights from the 1995-96 NHL season. Narrated by Don Cherry. Hi folks, you're going to love ROCK' EM SOCK' EM 8. My son Tim and I have screened hundreds of games to bring you the very best goals, hits, saves & bloopers, and my pick of the best Coaches Corner, plus some of my great openings of the games for Hockey Night In Canada. This year as a bonus I will have a few tips on how to run a practice for the coaches and some advice for the Players. Who could ask for anything more? No wonder ROCK' EM SOCK' EMS are the biggest selling tapes of all time. ROCK' EM SOCK' EM 8 you're gonna love it!
title: Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Hockey 8
